      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "the Cincinnati Office with the enclosed letter and envelope received",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "anonymously at the [REDACTED] in an envelope postmarked 7-3-52",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "at Cincinnati, Ohio.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "It will be noted that the enclosed letter is written in the German",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "language, and I am also enclosing a rather loose translation of the letter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "as furnished by the [REDACTED].",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "In view of the widespread interest in so-called \"flying saucers,\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "I am forwarding this material to the Bureau, with the thought in mind that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "the Bureau may desire to have a careful translation made of the attached",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "letter, and the results, if deemed advisable, made available to other",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
